summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department, accepting from ZymoGenetics, Inc., a Washington corporation, an easement for the Volunteer Park Reservoir water drain pipe, over portions of Lot 8, Block 11, East Park Addition to The City of Seattle and Lot 14, Block 68, Lake Union Shore Lands, all in Section 29, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M., King County, Washington.
